'''天使少女组'''（{{lang-en|Angel's Friends}}）是由[[Simona_Ferri|Simona Ferri]]制作的魔法少女题材的意大利漫画系列，于2007年初次公布。同名动画系列于2009年12月在[[Italia_1|Italia 1]]频道开始播放。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tvblog.it/post/16064/angels-friends-in-onda-dal-12-ottobre-su-italia1|title=''Angel's Friends'' in onda dal 12 ottobre su Italia1.|last=Camerino|first=Francesca|date=12 October 2009|language=it|accessdate=2016-04-17|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205085406/https://www.tvblog.it/post/16064/angels-friends-in-onda-dal-12-ottobre-su-italia1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 长达52集的第二季动画于2011年1月被宣布播放<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://finanza.repubblica.it/News_Dettaglio.aspx?code=641&dt=2011-01-12&src=TLB|title=Mondo TV, accordo con Play Entertainment per 2^ serie Angel's Friends|date=12 January 2011|accessdate=14 January 2012|language=it|archive-date=2013-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928023356/http://finanza.repubblica.it/News_Dettaglio.aspx?code=641&dt=2011-01-12&src=TLB|dead-url=no}}</ref>并于2012年4月29日在俄罗斯首次上映。<ref name="multimania">{{Cite news|url=http://angels-friends-world.blogspot.it/2012/04/blog-post_20.html|title=Второй сезон "Друзей Ангелов" на Мультимании (The second season of "Angel's Friends" to air on Multimania)|date=20 April 2012|language=ru|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928021138/http://angels-friends-world.blogspot.it/2012/04/blog-post_20.html|archive-date=2013-09-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

电视电影《天使少女组－在梦想与现实之间》（{{lang-en|Angel's Friends: Between Dream and Reality}}；{{lang-it|Angel's Friends – Tra Sogno e Realtà}}），于2011年四月23日上映。<ref name="film">{{Cite news|url=http://www.licensingitalia.it/news/anteprima_tv_del_film_di_angels_friend_1770.html|title=Anteprima TV del film di ''Angel's Friends''.|date=8 April 2011|work=Licensing Italia|language=it|access-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120115135759/http://www.licensingitalia.it/news/anteprima_tv_del_film_di_angels_friend_1770.html|archive-date=2012-01-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

